<chapter id="Fees_and_Charges">
  <title>Fees and Charges</title>

  <section id="FB" role="TOPIC">
    <title>Fees and Charges</title>

    <para role="TEXT"><variablelist>
        <varlistentry>
          <term>
            <guimenuitem moreinfo="none">The Fees and Charges module is used
            to</guimenuitem>
          </term>

          <listitem>
            <para role="TEXT">View all existing Fees,</para>
          </listitem>

          <listitem>
            <para role="TEXT">View all existing Bank Invoices,</para>
          </listitem>

          <listitem>
            <para role="TEXT">View, pay and submit Bank Invoices not paid
            yet,</para>
          </listitem>

          <listitem>
            <para role="TEXT">Edit the details of a Bank Invoices and submit
            them to the bank.</para>
          </listitem>
        </varlistentry>
      </variablelist></para>

    <section role="ITEM">
      <title>Fee Inquiry</title>

      <para>To navigate to the<emphasis role="bold"> Fee Inquiry function
      </emphasis>, from the tool bar, select Account Services &gt; Fees and
      Charges. Then select Fee Inquiry from the left side navigation
      menu.</para>

      <para>To use this function, click the Search Options link to display the
      fields that can be used to filter the list. These are<emphasis
      role="bold"> Entity, Bank, Customer ID, Product, Transaction Date,
      Amount, Fee Status</emphasis> fields.</para>

      <para>The column returned in the list of Fee records are the
      following:</para>

      <informaltable role="TEXT">
        <tgroup cols="2">
          <colspec colname="c1" colwidth="2.0*"/>

          <colspec colname="c2" colwidth="8.0*"/>

          <thead>
            <row>
              <entry valign="top"><para role="TEXT">Field</para></entry>

              <entry valign="top"><para role="TEXT">Description</para></entry>
            </row>
          </thead>

          <tbody>
            <row>
              <entry valign="top"><para role="TEXT"> <guilabel
              moreinfo="none">Customer ID</guilabel> </para></entry>

              <entry valign="top"><para role="TEXT">Customer id for which the
              fees have been computed. </para></entry>
            </row>

            <row>
              <entry valign="top"><para role="TEXT"> <guilabel
              moreinfo="none">Product</guilabel> </para></entry>

              <entry valign="top"><para role="TEXT">Product for which the fees
              has been computed </para></entry>
            </row>

            <row>
              <entry valign="top"><para role="TEXT"> <guilabel
              moreinfo="none">Fee Description </guilabel> </para></entry>

              <entry valign="top"><para role="TEXT">Description defined for
              the fee. </para></entry>
            </row>

            <row>
              <entry valign="top"><para role="TEXT"> <guilabel
              moreinfo="none">Ccy</guilabel> </para></entry>

              <entry valign="top"><para role="TEXT">Currency in which the fee
              has been computed.</para></entry>
            </row>

            <row>
              <entry valign="top"><para role="TEXT"> <guilabel
              moreinfo="none">Amount</guilabel> </para></entry>

              <entry valign="top"><para role="TEXT">Fee amount which has been
              computed.</para></entry>
            </row>

            <row>
              <entry valign="top"><para role="TEXT"> <guilabel
              moreinfo="none">Recalc Amount</guilabel> </para></entry>

              <entry valign="top"><para role="TEXT">Fee amount which has been
              optimized.</para></entry>
            </row>

            <row>
              <entry valign="top"><para role="TEXT"> <guilabel
              moreinfo="none">Transaction Reference</guilabel> </para></entry>

              <entry valign="top"><para role="TEXT">Unique Transaction
              reference number to identify the transaction.</para></entry>
            </row>

            <row>
              <entry valign="top"><para role="TEXT"> <guilabel
              moreinfo="none">Transaction Date</guilabel> </para></entry>

              <entry valign="top"><para role="TEXT">Date on which transaction
              happened.</para></entry>
            </row>

            <row>
              <entry valign="top"><para role="TEXT"> <guilabel
              moreinfo="none">Settlement Date</guilabel> </para></entry>

              <entry valign="top"><para role="TEXT">Settlement Date received
              from Back Office.</para></entry>
            </row>

            <row>
              <entry valign="top"><para role="TEXT"> <guilabel
              moreinfo="none">Status</guilabel> </para></entry>

              <entry valign="top"><para role="TEXT">The status of the fees.
              (Charged, Not Charged, Invoiced, etc...).</para></entry>
            </row>
          </tbody>
        </tgroup>
      </informaltable>
    </section>

